{"tid":893840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「真．長髮公主」15年沒剪髮　洗頭1次要用7罐洗髮精！","createTime":"2018-11-08T03:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:56:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c2731579404a77bfc31edd9a34c6bc15fc7ed2a5","tid":893840,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:00:13.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一名女子自12歲開始留頭髮後，已15年沒有剪過頭髮，目前她的頭髮已長到近乎及地，被許多人稱為「真人版長髮公主」，而她也成為網紅在Instagram上分享自己的日常，吸引近20萬名粉絲追蹤。<br />\n <br />\n綜合外媒報導，27歲的古巴諾娃（Dashik Gubanova Freckle）一開始喜歡短髮也留著短髮，12歲那年她和朋友打賭留長髮，沒想到卻從此愛上長髮和蓄髮，從此不再剪頭髮。<br />\n <br />\n隨著古巴諾娃長年蓄髮，她的生活也越來越不便，她透露，自己每天都要花1、2個小時梳開頭髮避免打結，洗頭髮時要用掉7罐洗髮精，吹乾頭髮時也要花上好幾個小時，更因此長年肩頸痠痛，但古巴諾娃對一切痛苦和麻煩都甘之如飴。<br />\n <br />\n目前古巴諾娃希望能繼續蓄髮，直到所有頭髮都能及地，之後才會考慮剪髮、捐出去做成假髮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gn3nrPq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGn3nrPq.png&h=7943eb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jd92rPw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJd92rPw.png&h=aa1a5376&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AyUhZ9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAyUhZ9z.png&h=960f6b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Rdbj9B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Rdbj9B.png&h=1ee26ed0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d582e4f5b28211cb59f18c58df8881eb970d28c9","tid":893840,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c98fc3a5354728db91a7225e7caf8155de0e2b3","tid":893840,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"髮交"},{"pid":"1f30e08e1271e3e9fb8b78338c1e987a00d968fc","tid":893840,"uid":37733,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:02:37.000Z","msg":"靚咩？"},{"pid":"6a2def7a852b5ce2f76e59069b04373